## Support and Issues

For issues on the stable release:
1. Use the bug report template
2. Include version: `git describe --tags --always`
3. Provide logs from: `$GAIA_GO_HOME/logs/`
4. Do NOT report issues from development branches

For new features or development questions:
- Use feature branches from feature/phase9-consolidation-*
- Follow the multi-session work SOP in CLAUDE.md
- Discuss significant changes before implementation

## Release Checklist

Before releasing a new stable version:
- [ ] All unit tests pass
- [ ] Integration tests pass  
- [ ] Load test with expected concurrent sessions
- [ ] Documentation updated
- [ ] CHANGELOG.md entry added
- [ ] Version number incremented
- [ ] Release tagged with git tag
- [ ] stable-phase# branch created/updated
- [ ] Release notes published

To create a stable release:
```bash
# From feature/phase9-consolidation-* (after final merges)
git tag -a v0.1.1-phase9 -m "Release v0.1.1-phase9 - [description]"
git push origin v0.1.1-phase9

# Create/update stable branch
git branch -f stable-phase9
git push -u origin stable-phase9

# Announce the release
```

